headline.main: 150th Anniversary: 1851-2001; After the Birthday Party: NYT@150 Online, and in Bookstores

lead_paragraph: This section will remain available online, with links to special multimedia features -- including audio interviews with many of the writers, a video tour of New York City in 1851 and archival material about the history of The Times: www.nytimes.com/150
